<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="following-n">following <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'fɒləʊɪŋ/    美 /'fɑːloʊɪŋ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] [常用单数] 一群追随者 / 支持者：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The band has a big following in Europe.
这支乐队在欧洲有一大批追随者。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="the-following">the following</h3>
<p>1.<strong>下列；如下：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The following is about the BBC and some other broadcasting stations in Britain.
下面是关于BBC和其他一些英国广播电台的介绍。</p></div></div>